{
  "stem": "21308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was, of course, still living in Chatteris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was January when he took power, which he did lawfully by the Act of Enabling.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was working on a farm for the Charles family and it was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my job in the wintertime was looking after all the winter stock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, we had a lot-- we had a number of farms, but I worked on one which was called [INAUDIBLE] Farm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, we had a foreman who I worked under and who was virtually my boss.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father had died a couple of years before and things were very, very tight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my main consideration at that time was ensuring I kept my job and my income to help my widowed mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that didn't stop us reading the papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, we got filtered news.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was a hard life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --the effect of the war, First World War, the casualties, and I remember men being brought home on stretchers after they'd been in hospital for a year or two.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if it meant that there was going to be a stable Germany, then I didn't think anybody thought much else about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because although we'd had all this bashing up of the Jews and that, we understood that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't accept it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, it was-- to put it quite bluntly, it was bloody cruel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the fact of the matter is we were much more concerned with our own problems.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was a boy of 15.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the first things I think which really registered with us was the Crystal Night, the burning of the books, and the burning down the Reichstag, which was obviously engineered, and that dreadful trial of the Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
